                <h2>Nutritional Needs for Chickens</h2>
                <p>Proper nutrition is crucial for chickens to maintain their health and productivity:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Feed:</strong> Provide a balanced feed with essential nutrients including proteins, vitamins, and minerals.</li>
                    <li><strong>Grains:</strong> Offer grains such as corn and wheat as a supplement to their feed.</li>
                    <li><strong>Greens:</strong> Fresh greens like lettuce and spinach can be beneficial for their overall health.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Always ensure access to clean, fresh water to support optimal digestion and hydration.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

