                <h2>Ideal Environment for Chickens</h2>
                <p>Creating a suitable environment is essential for the well-being of your chickens:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Coop:</strong> Provide a well-ventilated, secure coop to protect chickens from weather and predators.</li>
                    <li><strong>Space:</strong> Ensure enough space for chickens to roam and peck. Overcrowding can lead to stress and health issues.</li>
                    <li><strong>Cleanliness:</strong> Regularly clean the coop to prevent the buildup of waste and the spread of diseases.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Provide adequate bedding material to keep the coop dry and comfortable.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

